  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hoodie Survivor:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Auto shooter score attack survival game where your character moves forward continuously and you control the direction of travel by rotating left and right </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are six levels in total with 3 different themes: field, desert and space.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shoot enemies and avoid different types of indestructible hazards</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Score 61 points to unlock the next level</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each level can be played forever to try to beat your high score</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Super Hoodie Bros:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2d platformer with claymation graphics and 2 different styles of play: Run and gun and wall jumping with double jumps and down pound attack</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hoodie Survivor:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Auto shooter score attack survival game where your character moves forward continuously and you control the direction of travel by rotating left and right </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are six levels in total with 3 different themes: field, desert and space.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shoot enemies and avoid different types of indestructible hazards</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Score 61 points to unlock the next level</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each level can be played forever to try to beat your high score</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Super Hoodie Bros:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2d platformer with claymation graphics and 2 different styles of play: Run and gun and wall jumping with double jumps and down pound attack</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
